Package: dppca
Title: Differentially Private PCA with Scree Plot and Score Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yejin", "Jo", email = "yejinjo0220@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Minwoo", "Kim", email = "mwkim.stat@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: Tools for performing end-to-end principal component analysis (PCA).
    It provides constructing scree plot and score-based visualizations
    under the constraint of differential privacy.
    The package provides non-private and private PC directions,
    DP scree estimators based on clipped means, Huber-type private means, and
    private winsorized means, as well as PC score visualizations based on 
    2D score histograms with additive and sparse DP mechanisms, 
    including group-wise visualizations.
